nameEntry.part: Western Australia Child Welfare Department's Annual Reports

biogHist.abstract: Western Australia Child Welfare Department's Annual Reports contain draft copies and correspondence relating to the preparation of annual reports of the Child Welfare Department in Western Australia (CWD). The file is in poor condition and has few page numbers. It is arranged in reverse date order, with newer entries appearing first. The file begins with a draft of the report for the five years ended 30 June 1946 and a complete, original version of the final report for that period.
